title: New: Julia Losfelt – Here To Stay
body:
Impressing with her debut solo track Away earlier in the year alongside a cover of Mount KImbie’s You Took Your Time, Parisian singer songwriter **Julia Losfelt** is back, with the magical Here To Stay.

Conjuring up a dreamy, very modern, atmosphere, tinged with touches of the likes of **XXYYXX** or **Beat Culture**. Check out _Here To Stay_ below.
